Hi, I phase 1’d EECS 16b the moment I could, but I was still placed on the waitlist. Currently, I’m around 200 on the waitlist, and I have chosen a regular lab section instead of lite. Is it likely that I will be enrolled? Should I switch into the lite section? It’s important I take this class in sp’ 21 so I’m kinda worried.
